    "deskripsi_bisnis": "PT Pollux Properties Indonesia Tbk, together with its subsidiaries, engages in the development, trading, leasing, and operation of real estate properties and related services in Indonesia. It operates through two segments: Rent Office Room and Office. The company develops apartments, condominiums, offices, shopping centers, hospitals, hotels, convention centers, housing, industrial estates, and facilities. It also purchases, sells, leases, and operates real estate properties, as well as offers real estate services, such as agents, real estate brokers, and purchasing intermediaries. In addition, the company engages in the construction, mining, and transportation businesses. The company was founded in 2014 and is based in Jakarta Selatan, Indonesia. PT Pollux Properties Indonesia Tbk operates as a subsidiary of PT Borneo Melawai Perkasa.",
